                <ol class="rotation-steps">
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Summon 3 Hydras immediately</strong> &mdash; Deploy all 3 Hydras at the start of combat. Position them strategically to maximize coverage across enemy positions.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Maintain Ice Armor</strong> &mdash; Keep Ice Armor active for constant barrier uptime. Provides both damage reduction and mana regeneration for sustained casting.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Fire Bolt filler</strong> &mdash; Between Hydra cooldowns, spam Fire Bolt for filler damage and Flameweaver stacks. Each cast increases your Hydra damage.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Recast Hydras as they expire</strong> &mdash; Monitor Hydra duration. Recast individual Hydras as they expire to maintain 3-Hydra uptime continuously.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Inferno for burst windows</strong> &mdash; Use Inferno during dense pack encounters or to burn down elites. The fiery serpent adds significant AoE burst damage.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Teleport for repositioning</strong> &mdash; Use Teleport to escape danger or reposition for better Hydra placement angles. Bounding Conduit provides bonus movement speed.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Flame Shield for emergencies</strong> &mdash; Pop Flame Shield when you take burst damage or need to tank one-shot mechanics. The immunity window can save your life.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
