                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Gloves of the Illuminator is mandatory.</strong>
                    <p>Without Gloves of the Illuminator, Hydra lacks the duration and additional heads needed for consistent damage. This unique is absolutely required for the build to function properly.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Hydra placement matters.</strong>
                    <p>Hydras have a fixed attack range. Position them strategically at choke points or near boss spawn points to maximize uptime on high-priority targets. Poor placement wastes damage.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Serpentine aspect is non-negotiable.</strong>
                    <p>Aspect of the Serpentine transforms Hydra from mediocre to excellent by adding persistent burning ground. Without it, the build lacks the damage-over-time needed for high-tier content.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Abuse the safe playstyle.</strong>
                    <p>Hydra Sorc is one of the safest builds in the game. You can stand at maximum range while your Hydras do the work. Use this to your advantage against dangerous bosses and mechanics.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
